stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Enabled: register() → PolicyRegistered
  Enabled --> Enabled: register() same id → PolicyUpdated (checksum recomputed)
  Enabled --> Disabled: disable() → PolicyDisabled
  Disabled --> Enabled: enable() → PolicyEnabled
  Enabled --> [*]: (definition retained in provider)

  note right of Enabled
    Only ENABLED policies whose scope matches participate in evaluation.
    Any register/enable/disable bumps the engine generation, invalidating
    the decision cache. Each policy carries an integrity checksum that
    verify() recomputes and compares. Evaluation itself never mutates a
    policy — it emits PolicyEvaluated (and PolicyRejected on deny).
  end note
